Subject: Error for failed to start a high performance web server during appliance boot
Description:
Hello,
as a Netwrix partner, i am trying to install on our systems the EP appliance using the version reported, but i cannot access the web interface: it seems the web server fails to start.
I can see the error for "failed to start a high performance web server" during the virtual appliance boot.

I tried both the VMWare and Hyper-v versions, and both have the same issue.

Please let me know what i can do to resolve.
Thank you.
Massimo.
Solution_Comment__c: The VM did not have 2 network cards attached. Once the customer's attached the 2nd network card the EPP VM booted correctly.
